    <h1>About DK App Tools</h1>
    <p>DK App Tools is an independent app studio for practical software, clear product pages, useful articles, and support that grows with real products.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="compact-panel about-panel">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <article>
        <strong>Practical apps</strong>
        <p>Each app should have a clear job, a real reason to exist, and a product page that helps people decide whether it fits their needs.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <strong>Clear information</strong>
        <p>Product pages, policies, and articles should explain what a tool does, what it does not do, and how to use it responsibly.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <strong>Real support pages</strong>
        <p>Support should stay close to the products that actually exist, with practical contact details and boundaries that are easy to understand.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <strong>Built to grow honestly</strong>
        <p>DK App Tools can grow over time, but the site should grow with real apps, real documentation, and useful updates rather than empty placeholders.</p>
      </article>
